snippet.title: Best VGM 1343 - Lunar : The Silver Star - Meryod
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 50 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2NfhrT3gQdY

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Sega CD
Lunar : The Silver Star (1992)
Meryod
Noriyuki Iwadare
